     <p>
      looking for the hole? where it probably came out. Just so I get this right, there are several of these little plugs that could blow if the pressure relief valve isn't working? Also, should I just not drive her in that cold of weather? use different oil then 40 weight? Let it warm up longer?
     </p>
     <p>
